    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual visual representing medical breakthroughs and hope. Imagine a vibrant, glowing network of interconnected molecular structures and DNA strands, subtly forming a silhouette of a human brain or heart. In the foreground, hands (diverse skin tones: Indian, Caucasian, African) are gently reaching towards this glowing network, symbolizing healing and discovery. Elements of advanced technology like microscopic views and abstract data flows are integrated into the background, hinting at scientific research. The color palette should be hopeful and bright, with blues, greens, and soft yellows. Avoid literal images of specific diseases or overly clinical settings. The composition should be artistic and inspiring, emphasizing global collaboration and the future of medicine.",
