      tokenOverview: "This article discusses multiple crypto entities. USDT (Tether) is a stablecoin pegged to the US Dollar, aiming to provide price stability. Bitcoin (BTC) is the first and largest cryptocurrency, often seen as digital gold. Ethereum (ETH) is a decentralized platform that enables smart contracts and decentralized applications, with Consensys being a major developer in its ecosystem.",
