      tradingVolume: "USDT consistently sees the highest daily trading volumes among all cryptocurrencies, often surpassing Bitcoin and Ethereum, due to its widespread use in trading pairs and remittances. Bitcoin and Ethereum also command significant daily trading volumes.",
