      ecosystemGrowth: "The Ethereum ecosystem, supported by Consensys, continues to grow with new dApps, Layer 2 solutions, and enterprise blockchain initiatives. The stablecoin ecosystem, led by USDT, expands with new use cases and integrations, especially in cross-border payments. Bitcoin\'s ecosystem is evolving with Lightning Network adoption and new development tools.",
