      tokenUtility: "ETH serves multiple critical functions within its ecosystem: it is used to pay for transaction fees (gas), stake to secure the network and earn rewards, and acts as the primary collateral asset in numerous Decentralized Finance (DeFi) protocols and NFT marketplaces. Its utility is foundational for the entire Ethereum-based digital economy.",
