      bullCase: "The bullish case hinges on Japan successfully navigating its inflation challenge, leading to a healthy normalization of monetary policy without stifling growth. This would signal global economic stability and potentially attract capital to developed markets. Concurrently, sustained and strategic SWF investments in AI could accelerate technological advancements globally, creating new economic opportunities and boosting productivity. For India, this could translate into increased demand for its skilled tech workforce and IT services, and potentially attract strategic investments into its own emerging AI ecosystem.",
