    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual visual representing capital flowing into a digital asset like Bitcoin. The image should feature abstract, glowing lines of light or energy converging into a stylized, translucent Bitcoin symbol. Emphasize the idea of \'trillions\' with subtle numerical elements or a sense of immense scale, perhaps with a backdrop of a global financial network. Use a dark, sophisticated color palette with contrasting bright accents for the \'flow\' of capital. The overall composition should be dynamic and forward-looking, conveying both the challenge and the potential of massive financial investment in cryptocurrency. Avoid any specific architectural or human elements, focusing purely on abstract financial concepts and digital growth.",
