    outlook: "The future outlook suggests a continued, albeit potentially volatile, integration of disruptive technology companies into public markets, with AI and space tech leading the charge. We anticipate more innovative financing and transaction methods, where private equity and cryptocurrencies play a more prominent role alongside traditional fiat currencies. Regulatory frameworks will likely evolve to accommodate these shifts, aiming to balance innovation with investor protection and market stability. The convergence of high-tech IPOs and alternative asset adoption is expected to redefine capital markets, creating both unprecedented opportunities and new challenges for investors and regulators alike.",
